{"tid":2084831,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[重po求推] 七一港島 街頭見 唔需要維園見 Be Water","createTime":"2020-06-29T13:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T02:02:14.000Z","uid":40431,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"e26842d8a1b5c6aab7e6ed28eb957e262d6759ac","tid":2084831,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"抗爭咗足足一年，幾時先真正學識<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">BE WATER</span></strong><br />\n冇不反嘅遊行，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一係入唔到維園，一係出唔到維園</strong></span><br />\n524係一個好好嘅教訓，起點一定大量SS同埋伏，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係最危險嘅地方</span></strong><br />\nSOGO已經算開揚，維園啲出入口咁窄，人多少少都塞住，一亂真係仆得街<br />\n<br />\n港島條路咁長，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>唔一定要去維園</strong></span><br />\n一夠鐘行出嚟，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>邊度少popo就去邊度</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">人群處於一個流動嘅狀態，有popo就四散，冇popo就聚集</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好俾一個固定地方對家提早部署</span></strong><br />\n咁先係真正BE WATER<br />\n<br />\n既然已經冇不反，根本冇可能好似以往嘅七一遊行咁行一條固定路線<br />\n所謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>送頭</strong></span>唔係話出嚟就係送頭<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係明知一個地方極高危都照去</strong></span><br />\n希望咁多位手足真係三思<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我哋七一港島街頭見就得，唔駛維園見</strong></span>，popo有本事就成個香港島封咗佢<br />\n<br />\n見到好多po都仲叫緊七一維園見<br />\n真係唔好再流於<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">形式主義</span></strong><br />\n我知過去七一都係維園出發，有象徵意義<br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今時唔同往日</strong></span><br />\n講咗一年<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">BE WATER</span></strong>，今次七一就唔好得個講字啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">七一 街頭見</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ed5vv7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fed5vv7J.jpg&h=00cdba11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"548c3cd8f40f1b33f58ea61b35682f33660013e5","tid":2084831,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6003a2c0b7d619516e2548128223cd14e00c3b","tid":2084831,"uid":40431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:22:07.000Z","msg":"七一 街頭見"},{"pid":"984a0f9bfc3d84dd6d610d96968919c86dcb30cf","tid":2084831,"uid":40431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"香港要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2b55d3bf430e779fcef15889dbeddf185d6dfe","tid":2084831,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Q42Hko_IIk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6Q42Hko_IIk&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=7149c899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Q42Hko_IIk</a>"},{"pid":"edd348e57083bd7aadcaa71492e3b5b4897d402f","tid":2084831,"uid":152394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8344cf70a1af62b9a597fe1706015fd2aa6632a3","tid":2084831,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b5b4b26f4195c967271780e3db9b5518a0d3d69","tid":2084831,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"出咗嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088ddf1285be98e88f9a3ad2edbda54cd9aad1b9","t